{"tid":1299782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毛澤東：如敵人把我們說得一塌糊塗，一無是處，那就更好了","createTime":"2019-07-09T07:07:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T07:37:15.000Z","uid":62257,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5c2de46fbc551f02e2d25a528f6fa90c9a6ea178","tid":1299782,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:07:58.000Z","msg":"毛主席語錄：<br />\n<br />\n我認為，對我們來說，一個人，一個黨，一個軍隊，或者一個學校，如若不被敵人反對，那就不好了，那一定是與敵人同流合污了。如若被敵人反對，那就好了，那就證明我們同敵人劃清界限了。如若敵人起勁地反對我們，把我們說得一塌糊塗，一無是處，那就更好了，那就證明我們不但同敵人劃清了界限，而且證明我們的工作是很有成績的了。"},{"pid":"a9390d00b52d162a64b6d7f7ab37c9490d23fa2d","tid":1299782,"uid":62257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:09:51.000Z","msg":"肥佬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e634a826ff7ee96365f6465aaeadafe5a04a80f3","tid":1299782,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:10:28.000Z","msg":"少左人屌林鄭林鄭做錯了"},{"pid":"abc7ac71eaa526f4904fecbc29c13f82a57611c9","tid":1299782,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:11:09.000Z","msg":"《一日爭取唔到真普選，我地永遠處於被動》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299151</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"029e8c5d08139b6704e2d377568358b525d726b4","tid":1299782,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4565de23a6ab44408f6504516466b26b0328c172","tid":1299782,"uid":105715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:15:39.000Z","msg":"曾鈺成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef83feaf46d75d6b095595bd772eb94dc7e8213a","tid":1299782,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e634a826ff7ee96365f6465aaeadafe5a04a80f3","tid":1299782,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime